; The term "component details" refers to the component's ID, product line ID, product line name, and device name; 
; "Usage patterns" include total usage, latest usage start date, earliest usage end date, and average stock; 
; "Supplier performance" encompasses supplier ID, supplier name, average supply, total inventory count, and average lead time; 
; "Recent access information" includes last access date, user name, and total access time; 
; The sorting is based on the total usage in descending order (i.e., highest usage first) and average lead time in ascending order (i.e., shortest lead time first).
